{"tid":496031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李兆富今入稟高院控告葉劉淑儀誹謗","createTime":"2017-12-11T09:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T11:50:02.000Z","uid":41404,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"53d415a8a82aa6b8d45c2036c19a77f5d287619c","tid":496031,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T09:55:10.000Z","msg":"新民黨主席兼行會成員葉劉淑儀，日前稱領展通過專欄作家李兆富對她出言恐嚇，並引述該黨政策總裁袁彌昌指，李曾稱「叫葉劉唔好再搞喇喎，再搞會郁佢啲區議員㗎喇」。李兆富今日委託律師入稟高院，告葉劉誹謗，要求索償。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉日前在立法會會議廳外見記者時，近來或因她常常在專欄和立法會批評領展，遭「領展派人恐嚇我」，引述該黨政策總裁袁彌昌稱，早前遭專欄作家李兆富恐嚇。領展行政總裁王國龍事後通過鄉議局主席劉業強，邀約葉劉吃飯「擺平」事件遭拒。李兆富當時否認恐嚇，領展則對指控感到震驚，聲稱不會通過任何人，向該黨表達有關言論。<br />\n葉劉的言論亦引來警方主動了解，後來葉劉澄清她所講的「『郁』字係我感覺」、「冇可能講exact wording」，又指領展方面沒有再聯絡她，認為「一人一句不如交畀警方調查」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171211/57568190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F57568190&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANni7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=0b2c3227\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F57568190&h=db83c9ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171211/57568190</a>"},{"pid":"ec6d5c84d4ed23398f66b9d868d8b1f634d97f47","tid":496031,"uid":66514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:02:02.000Z","msg":"兩個床上解決啦！"},{"pid":"a23e7c241af58a776941e53845f79a7ad0906009","tid":496031,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:11:37.000Z","msg":"&quot;葉劉的言論亦引來警方主動了解，後來葉劉澄清她所講的「『郁』字係我感覺」、「冇可能講exact wording」&quot;<br />\n<br />\n縮得太遲"},{"pid":"318bb16f01d139841aa0b542d046cdffef862b4e","tid":496031,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:15:40.000Z","msg":"保安局局長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民政事務局局長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老董果批人既質素"},{"pid":"00ddb6990967b76de00453b44555e92c4af62816","tid":496031,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩個床上解決啦！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d9e39d9b52b6a4e0ce651ed367eda0c26bde4f","tid":496031,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:18:38.000Z","msg":"metoo佢啦葉師奶，係我就唔忍啦"},{"pid":"be0233946ea90458e823cd1a39dff4ac126c3bec","tid":496031,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:20:56.000Z","msg":"富仔ho ball"},{"pid":"064f32cfc66bd22060cc97ee4cce56242b17ba93","tid":496031,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:23:48.000Z","msg":"依次真係狗咬狗喇"},{"pid":"53160935b58909386c3525e02c3942ee5a5cbd13","tid":496031,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:50:03.000Z","msg":"專欄作家李兆富入稟控告新民黨主席葉劉淑儀誹謗。<br />\n<br />\n李兆富接受查詢時說，葉劉淑儀兩次在立法會大樓回應記者時，就有關他的說話內容失實。他相信法律公正，自己沒講過的話，不可由他人塞進自己口。<br />\n<br />\n李兆富要求葉劉淑儀停止再作出有關的失實言論，他說，入稟狀未有要求金錢賠償，亦無提及對其名譽損害如何處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1369485-20171211.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1369485-20171211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANni7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f15b2ce5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1369485-20171211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=042c2704\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1369485-20171211.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"33fde0ef13bf4296e3b8d535508517840e99191d","tid":496031,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:54:49.000Z","msg":"我地都係葉劉淑儀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f82970c12552bb3be9bfcd51fcfa3d26f799e2e","tid":496031,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>專欄作家李兆富入稟控告新民黨主席葉劉淑儀誹謗。<br />\n<br />\n李兆富接受查詢時說，葉劉淑儀兩次在立法會大樓回應記者時，就有關他的說話內容失實。他相信法律公正，自己沒講過的話，不可由他人塞進自己口。<br />\n<br />\n李兆富要求葉劉淑儀停止再作出有關的失實言論，他說，入稟狀未有要求金錢賠償，亦無提及對其名譽損害如何處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1369485-20171211.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1369485-20171211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANni7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f15b2ce5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1369485-20171211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=042c2704\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1369485-20171211.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a></blockquote><br />\n如果最後話有關言論不屬誹謗，咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08a573ef98877a3cd2c14854a81b2c692c930cf","tid":496031,"uid":54627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:00:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兩個床上解決啦！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/190051_ca90c26c8d94a7933996f9bced6ae8b9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F190051_ca90c26c8d94a7933996f9bced6ae8b9.gif&h=450a60c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"543809cae209036dd3fcff8db22c7042d6f858aa","tid":496031,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地都係葉劉淑儀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係你老豆"},{"pid":"ce089999e6f7c8033674381650b422b3ce